Overall requirements: Fitness app that records your workouts while a voice coach speaks to you. After recording you will be able to upload videos onto Facebook and challenge friends to do the same.

Basic Functionatities:
1) Camera recording within app - Willis
2) Integration to facebook to upload files - Susan

Secondary Functionalities:
3) Play audio file while recording
4) Creating a database for audio files and graphics (Creating Samples)

Other Functionalities:
5) UI - Log in and navigation through app
6) UI - Graphics and logo
7) Newer functionality and versions



